Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.97,0:03:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是OZ第一部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告接近中的穿梭機
