Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再接近\N我們就會開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是恐嚇，是警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管，開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接近中的飛行物體爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變型了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!攻擊攻擊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人機動戰士中彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去平衡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.74,0:04:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是鋼彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種攻擊根本不能擊倒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我天真嗎?技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再倚靠他們的力量會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和鋼彈有關的人還有利用價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,01的駕駛員
