Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們現在不能輕舉妄動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特和麥丘留士量產型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生產準備在月面基地那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在照預定計劃進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經不需要他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何討厭他們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫉妒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種感情我不敢恭維啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說!我為何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!有緊急聯絡進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,07U1地點的資源衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以往的資料裡沒有的新鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星和發現它的部隊一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被鋼彈消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.26,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你為何知道\N那是鋼彈的所為
