Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD不能調離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地的防守崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派拜葉特和麥丘留士出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
