Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來有事發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相當驚徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.93,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身份不明的鋼彈\N宣佈要消滅衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身份不明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是新機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特徵呢?武器呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有甚麼詳細情報嗎?
