Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在去確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的把衛星毀滅了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要看資源衛星的規模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但預測破壞力\N就要看它的設計圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他造出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們五人研究的鋼彈的原型嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點危險的氣息啊
