Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他裝上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.45,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道?還是失控了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在做連我們也猶豫的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.12,0:08:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一兩個衛星真的會被毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來，1號
