Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2號比1號優良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我應付今次的對手吧
