Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的駕駛員今次或許也會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為對手是鋼彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是新機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一部就令OZ的部隊全軍覆沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特徵呢?武器呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是執行任務的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題和技師們的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它和那部叫\N麥丘留士的紅色傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會旗鼓相當吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想來也要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫鋼彈駕駛員自相殘殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你就坐山觀虎門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，1號，不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是機動戰士的性能測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要幫手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們乖乖地不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚會輪到你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是挖空心思的戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也須要提防他已經是敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用那麼擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他能信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為出賣我們的人不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶這種巧妙的東西來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有張五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師O把這個交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用它來解悶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特和麥丘留士的運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩部機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.95,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐和五飛的鋼彈被改良了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而新的鋼彈一定是卡特爾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時機或許來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和卡特爾會合後就反擊OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何能斷定他是自己人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推測會產生錯誤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我們現在駕駛OZ的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據情況也可能會戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是強大的自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就能如你所言反擊OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那部鋼彈\N只有輕微的攻擊力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就毀滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛伏在OZ的你在收拾特列斯前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隱藏你的身份是優先的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你一直知道的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也好，戰鬥看看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平民避難完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人從哪裡出現也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防守別鬆懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一區正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.96,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二區正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個衛星裝有外部雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何敵人來襲也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個衛星能保衛自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星06E3注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在要毀滅衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止無謂的反抗，馬上撤離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆，馬上撤離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎擊!外部雷射砲準備發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怕死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，不要戰鬥就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.93,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪啊，我在流淚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我毫不傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那衛星已經無法挽救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.89,0:14:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說接著會毀滅這空域的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用運輸機前去太引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由這裡起用機動戰士移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是確認鋼彈的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，有需要時就戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但對手是卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用杞人憂天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，小心行事，有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他…把衛星毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們引開敵人的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.73,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥丘留士單獨行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它一出現就毀滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太放任前鋼彈駕駛員自由行動了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它自爆裝置的開關在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.65,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而現在\N他的眼裡只是看見鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會清楚看見敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞一個月後完成啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾也行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又會忙起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會把...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.81,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身份不明的機動戰士為自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那部鋼彈在消滅OZ啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是就最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.86,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容設施的空氣提供系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫技師長\N你做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是載斷了監獄的空氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有收到任何指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有蕾蒂‧安特校的批准嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,批準由我來下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是遵從正確的指示啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.73,0:17:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安小姐太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，年紀有點大了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙腳站不穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，那是缺氧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你發覺了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為你操心才那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想讓你老人家擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有30分鍾嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遣憾的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.88,0:17:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神和神龍的改良還未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想死的人就快點去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別浪費空氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頑強的老人會被討厭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生不頑強就不能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…他想我們死得安心點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.64,0:17:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日畢竟由我代希洛出擊就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做甚麼?五飛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今，那種東西有等於沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想活得久一點，你就別出聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.42,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但沒有奇蹟發生\N我們就死定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是為了有奇蹟發生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做現在能做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我現在要退出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.20,0:18:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒出息的死法，我真丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外部看來沒有動態反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它真的在這種地方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.62,0:18:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會已經去了其他空域嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會，鋼彈一定在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星不需要這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡!是鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在衛星裡
